        "action": "Split motorcycle and car driver licenses.",
        "additional_details": "I got 6 penalty points and a fine for speeding on my motorcycle (my fault for speeding) and now my insurance will go up on both my motorcycle and car insurance. Why should I be hit twice?",
        "background": "If you\u2019re one of thousands  (possibly millions) of dual drivers (car & motorcycle) and you get a driving penalty using either it\u2019ll impact you twice! Insurance on both means will increase and points are applicable to your whole license. This is double punishment and can impact your work/family",
